des:
RSMART products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your RSMART products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "RSMART" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one RSMART account in our " RSMART" app;
(3). You need to have some RSMART devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " RSMART" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "RSMART" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "RSMART" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "RSMART", and you'll be navigated to RSMART login page;
(9). Input your RSMART account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
